The paper discusses the ranking of Communication journals using bibliometric tools, which involves analyzing and measuring scientific publications. This falls under the scope of several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.DL (Digital Libraries), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). However, since the paper focuses on the analysis of scientific publications, cs.DL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.SI, cs.CL, and cs.CR.
